title: File:Threlkeld Quarry Steam Galas CSR No. 19.jpg
author: ARG_Flickr
description: The fifth of the guest locomotives, Hudswell, Clarke and Company 1056 Lautoka No. 19, seen here by the water tower down at the shed was another from Statfold Barn Railway. Built in 1914 it used to work in the sugar cane fields of Fiji.
